highlights.text: KPop Demon Hunters Cast has the most spots on Viral Songs Singapore. “Golden” is the highest at #4.
“MOVE” by Lecrae and 1K Phew is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Singapore, up 21 spots at #73.
“有一种遗憾叫我们” by 田园 has been on Viral Songs Singapore the longest, at 107 days straight.
“BOYtude” by idntt is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Singapore at #91.
